&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Band 5 Staff Nurse - Adult Day Surgery Unit (ADSU)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The Adult Day Surgery Unit comprises of 34 day case beds. We care for patients undergoing day case procedures in a variety of surgical specialties including urology, plastics, orthopaedics, general surgery, maxilo facial, ENT and trauma. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We are open Monday to Friday 07:30 to 22:00 and Saturdays 07:00 to 16:00. We are a dynamic unit and strive to deliver a positive patient experience.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We offer flexible working through the self-rostering system and provide opportunities for nurses to develop both professionally and personally, through local training and external professional courses.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sister Charlotte Maddocks on 0118 322 7622 or charlotte.maddocks@royalberkshire.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
